tf.autograph.set_verbosity(0, alsologtostdout=True)
test_fn = Dispatcher('test_fn')
@test_fn.register(gpflow.inducing_variables.InducingVariables)
def test_iv(x):
    return tf.reduce_sum(x.Z)
test_fn_compiled = tf.function(test_fn)
result = test_fn_compiled(gpflow.inducing_variables.InducingPoints([1.0, 2.0]))
assert result.numpy() == 3.0
captured = capsys.readouterr()
tf_warning = (
    'WARNING:.*Entity .* appears to be a generator function. It will not be converted by AutoGraph.'
    )
assert bool(re.match(tf_warning, captured.out)) == expect_autograph_warning
pytest.mark.parametrize('Dispatcher, expect_autograph_warning', [(
    multipledispatch.Dispatcher, True), (gpflow.utilities.Dispatcher, False)])
